title: ~Survey~ Help for English class, pls
body:
Hey guys, Malcantor here. If you have yet to participate in my League survey for my English class, I would greatly appreciate it! I am examining correlations between player communication and skill level. I only have a few days left and I already have the preliminary data analysis done. The survey can be located at: 

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1FuvSkVsEmVFB6nNL5vJtrDimjN0_isCzSIQ7OIRJ2Ww/viewform

if you so desire to help me . Thank you in advance. 
-Michael

replies.body: Would love to help you, but i'm not a ranked player.  Good luck though!

Already filled out. Good luck on your project!
-Sebastian

done
